<taxonomicName authorityName="Lucas" authorityYear="1845" box="[462,630,1671,1696]" class="Malacostraca" family="Vibiliidae" genus="Vibilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amphipoda" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="jeangerardi">
<emphasis box="[462,630,1671,1696]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">V. jeangerardi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
could not be found at the MNHN and is considered lost. Although the description and figures by 
<bibRefCitation author="Lucas, H." box="[732,886,1711,1737]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" refId="ref37948" refString="Lucas, H. (1846) Les amphipodes. Histoire naturelle des animaux articules, premiere partie Crustaces, Arachnides, Myriapodes et Hexapodes. Exploration scientifique de I'Algerie pendant les annees 1840, 1841, 1842. Paris, pp. 51 - 56, pl. 5." type="journal volume" year="1846">Lucas (1846)</bibRefCitation>
are inadequate, the status of this, relatively common, Mediterranean species has been established by 
<bibRefCitation author="Marion, A. F." box="[1022,1196,1751,1777]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" pagination="1 - 19" refId="ref38038" refString="Marion, A. F. (1874) Recherches sur les animaux inferieurs du golfe de Marseille. Descriptions des Crustaces Amphipodes parasites des salpes. Annales des Sciences naturelles (Tome 1), sixieme serie. Zoologie et Paleontologie, serie 5, 17, 1 - 19, pls 1, 2." type="book chapter" year="1874">Marion (1874)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Bovallius, C." pageId="12" pageNumber="13" pagination="1 - 72" refId="ref35551" refString="Bovallius, C. (1887 c) Contributions to a monograph of the Amphipoda Hyperiidea, Part I: 1. The families Tyronidae, Lanceolidae and Vibilidae. Kongliga Svenska Vetenskaps-Akademiens Handlingar, 21 (5), 1 - 72, pls 1 - 10." type="journal article" year="1887">Bovallius (1887c)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Chevreux, E." box="[421,628,1791,1817]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" pagination="1 - 195" refId="ref36051" refString="Chevreux, E. (1900) Amphipodes provenant des campagnes de I'Hirondelle (1885 - 1888). Resultats des Campagnes scientifiques accomplies sur son Yacht, par Albert 1 er, Prince Souverain de Monaco, 16 (i - iv), 1 - 195, pls 1 - 18." type="journal article" year="1900">Chevreux (1900)</bibRefCitation>
. The 
<typeStatus box="[712,762,1791,1817]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">type</typeStatus>
locality is the Mediterranean Sea, harbour at Bône, 
<collectingCountry box="[340,431,1831,1857]" name="Algeria" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Algeria</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
